summary: Ginnan - Ginnan is a charming cat with a unique story. He is the adopted brother of Kabosu, the Shiba Inu who became an internet sensation and the face of Dogecoin. Rescued and given a loving home by Kabosu's owner, Ginnan has brought joy and laughter to everyone who meets him. Our mission is to share Ginnan's delightful antics and heartwarming story with the world, spreading happiness and positivity one purr at a time. Join us on this journey and become a part of Ginnan's growing family of fans.
